description: This file is a C header (.h) file defining internal API function prototypes for the BREE Site Resource Manager component, including resource registration, unregistration, mapping, and loading functions.

methods.name: BreeSrmoRegisterCookedResource
methods.description: Registers a cooked resource within the BREE Site Resource Manager.

methods.name: BreeSrmoUnregisterCookedResource
methods.description: Unregisters a previously registered cooked resource.

methods.name: BreeSrmoMapCookedResource
methods.description: Maps a URL to a cooked resource handle.

methods.name: BreeSrmoLoadCookedResources
methods.description: Loads all cooked resources into the system.
